img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2361879429994aac0ca33e06673e9675ac3a6a7f","tid":1229663,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:00:37.000Z","msg":"無可能！<br />\n全香港有成700萬人係支持林鄭既<br />\n<br />\n你班比外國勢力入侵既傳媒一定係無計飛鴿傳書既訊息量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}